         Nahh, this was in response to people being able to already change their name for free.  It was an easy process.</P><P>1)Transfer char you want name changed to Legends.<BR>2)Have someone you know or yourself make a char with the name of the char you transfered to legends on your old server.<BR>3)transfer back the char from legends.  It appears with an x behind its name.  <BR>4) Petition and GM will change it.</P><P>Since people already figured out you could change your name this was free of charge, why not start up a service for the dumb people that didn't figure out you could do it this way and make money off them.</P><P>Niyqor the Malevolent<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
